    <p>My sin­cere wish for Ikhsan, and a sum­mary of ev­ery­thing I want to say about him, is that while many now know him as Fandi’s son, I hope one day, Fandi will be known as Ikhsan’s fa­ther.</p>
    <p>LAW AND HOME AF­FAIRS MIN­IS­TER</p>
    <p>K. SHAN­MUGAM, while con­grat­u­lat­ing na­tional team foot­baller Ikhsan Fandi (above), who was named Berita Har­ian’s Young Achiever of the Year.</p>

